steps: Elements of the Virtual Building > Construction Elements > Walls
description:
In ARCHICAD, you can draw walls that are straight, curved, trapezoidal and polygonal.

Wall structure can basic (of a single component), or composite (composed of several components). You can also create complex walls (Profile Wall) of any custom shape and with a combination of components. Like other construction elements, a Wallâ€™s essential structure derives from its Building Material.
